data.text:
CD Release event:

The NEW album "Don't Worry 'Bout Me - remembering Ella and Joe"

"One guitar, one voice. All swinging!"

Multiple-Award winning Jazz guitarist Terrence Brewer called upon jazz and blues vocalist Pamela Rose to lovingly rejoice in the vocal/guitar duo work of Ella Fitzgerald and Joe Pass. Mellifluous, swinging and intimate, Ella and Joes partnership on Pablo Records created four incomparable records, treasured by a generation of music lovers.

Brewer and Rose discovered that those recordings had been deeply influential to them both and embarked on a journey of rediscovery which has resulted in a new recording Dont Worry Bout Me Remembering Ella & Joe.
